description:
In this issue:

"Go-Man: Red's Story" by Bill Widener, Starlen Baxter and Heather Kennedy

"Random Thoughts: Part One" by Stephen Csutoras, Craig Gassen and Stefano Gaudiano

"Finster vs. Cockroach: Part Four" by Scott Parrish

"The Chosen" by Sarah Chamberlain and Guy Davis

"Fire Man" by R. G. Taylor and Robert "Rob" Walton

"Caliber Bonus: Ashes (Preview)" by John Bergin

NOTE: Issue 11 is mistakenly billed as issue 12 on the cover.

"Random Thoughts" by Stephen Csutoras, Craig Gassen and Stefano Gaudiano

"Gideon's: Headliner" by Randy Zimmerman and Jason Moore

"Home Fires: A Christopher Staff Story" by Richard G. Taylor

"Fugitive: Castaways" by Charles Marshall, James Tucker and Greg Cravens

"Street Shadows: Diner Life" by Kyle Garrett, Ken Landgraf and James Kessler

"Caliber Bonus: Boston Bombers (Preview)" by Ron Fortier, Christopher A. Jones and Gary Kato
Translates Wolverine: The Best There Is #7-12.
name: Wolverine der Best von Allen: Schluss mit Lustig
